summary: This fixes a bug in which you cannot buy conjuration spells because the original removed it from the game. This file replaces the Skyre module so the spells are not removed but just don't show up in the leveled spell list for vendors.
descriptionHtml:
This fixes a bug in the Insect Begone SkyRe patch, which crashes the game when you try to buy the conjuration spells: Cojure - Frostbite spider and Conjure - Large frostbite spider. This file replaces the Skyre module so the spells are not removed but just don't show up in the leveled spell list for vendors.

Original mod is required, but this file replaces the SkyRe module.
Get the original here: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26468]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26468[/url]
author: yroc1234
